      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "2",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "And Pilate asked him",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] This was a private investigation within the ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "prætorium",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", after the Jews, carefully suppressing ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "the religious grounds",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " on which they had condemned our Lord, had advanced against Him a triple accusation of (i) seditious agitation, (ii) prohibition of the payment of the tribute money, and (iii) the assumption of the suspicious title of “King of the Jews.” This was a ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
