        "class": "ital",
        "text": "political",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " charge, and one which Pilate could not overlook. Having no ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "quæstor",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " to conduct the examination, he was obliged to hear the case in person.",
        "children": []
      },
